     A            F2BARC        12A  B  5  9COLOR(WHT)
     A*
     A          R FMT300
     A                                      CF05
     A                                      CF07
     A                                      OVERLAY
     A                                  1  4' NON-CONFORMANCE SHEET '
     A                                      DSPATR(RI)
